\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The morning sunlight streamed through the classroom windows, casting a warm glow over the rows of desks. Haruki sat at her usual spot, her sketchbook open in front of her, pencil moving swiftly across the page. Instead of her classmates, the desks in her drawing were occupied by whimsical creatures\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 a fox with nine tails lounged in the corner, a dragon coiled around the teacher\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s podium, and a flock of tiny winged sprites flitted through the air. A smirk tugged at her lips as she added the finishing touches to a griffin perched smugly on Aiko\u8217\'92s desk.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko, seated beside her, leaned over to peek at the sketch. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You look unusually happy today,\u8221\'94 she noted, her tone equal parts curious and suspicious. \u8220\'93Did something good happen?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Across from them, Akihito sat with his arms crossed, half-listening while flipping through his own notebook. He raised an eyebrow at Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s expression but didn\u8217\'92t comment.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t look up, her pencil still moving. \u8220\'93I submitted my Career Plan,\u8221\'94 she said, her voice light and sing-songy.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes widened, and she practically shot forward in her chair. \u8220\'93You did?!\u8221\'94 she exclaimed, much too loud for the classroom. A few students glanced their way, but Aiko didn\u8217\'92t seem to care. \u8220\'93What did you pick?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki finally looked up, drawing out the moment with an infuriatingly smug grin. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Tokyo University,\u8221\'94 she said, pausing dramatically. \u8220\'93Fine Arts program.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko and Akihito reacted at the same time\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What?!\u8221\'94 Aiko gasped, her eyes sparkling with surprise.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93WHAT?!\u8221\'94 Akihito groaned, his tone laced with horror.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Meanwhile, Akihito rubbed his temples as if physically pained. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Look, I know you\u8217\'92re impulsive and stubborn as a mule, but I didn\u8217\'92t think you\u8217\'92d just }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 impulsively decide the trajectory of your career in a day, let alone from my off-hand remarks.}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 He stared at her in disbelief.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki scoffed, half-annoyed. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Look, you were the one who suggested Tokyo University yesterday!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93}{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Suggested!}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 Akihito emphasized the word. \u8220\'93I was thinking at least you\u8217\'92d put it into consideration as }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 one}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  of your choices, not }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 nose-dive}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  into it!\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But I }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 want}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  to go to Tokyo University,\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 Haruki said, as if it were the most obvious thing in the world.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito exhaled sharply, pinching the bridge of his nose. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Look\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 \u8221\'94 he started, his voice filled with exasperation. \u8220\'93Did at least your parents approve of it?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No,\u8221\'94 Haruki said in a sing-songy tone.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito stared at her, deadpan. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Of course.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko snorted, clapping Haruki on the back. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, you\u8217\'92re in for an interesting conversation at home.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki grinned, twirling her pencil between her fingers. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, I\u8217\'92m well aware.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito groaned, dropping his head onto his desk in defeat, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re crazy.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki shrugged, her pencil still moving. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Maybe. But it\u8217\'92s my future, not theirs.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko leaned back in her chair, running a hand through her hair. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Wow. I mean, I knew you were stubborn, but this is next level. What are you going to do when they find out?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s smile faltered for a moment, but she quickly recovered. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ll deal with it when the time comes,\u8221\'94 she said, her tone casual. \u8220\'93For now, I\u8217\'92m just happy I finally made a decision.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito shook his head. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re unbelievable, you know that? But hey, It takes guts to go after what you want.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki chuckled, her smug expression softening. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Thanks. That means a lot.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The bell rang, signaling the start of class, and the room filled with the sound of shuffling papers and murmured conversations. Haruki closed her sketchbook and tucked it into her bag, her mind already wandering to the future. For the first time in a long time, she felt like she was in control of her own destiny.}
