\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The school day had ended, and the hallways buzzed with the chatter of students heading to clubs, cram school, or home. Haruki stretched her arms above her head as she walked, a grin spreading across her face. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ahh, I\u8217\'92ve been waiting for this all week,\u8221\'94 she mused aloud. \u8220\'93Today\u8217\'92s the plein air session! I wonder where we\u8217\'92ll go this time. Maybe the riverside? Or that garden behind the old shrine? Ugh, I can\u8217\'92t wait to just sit outside and paint.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko trailed beside her, shaking her head. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re way too excited for someone who just turned their entire career plan into an act of rebellion.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Behind them, Akihito sighed, his hands stuffed into his pockets as he matched their pace. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I thought you\u8217\'92d at least talk with your parents and try to convince them, Haruki,\u8221\'94 he said, his tone serious. \u8220\'93Arguing against your parents is one thing, but going against them is another.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah,\u8221\'94 Aiko chimed in, nodding sagely. \u8220\'93You know, like, make a PowerPoint presentation or something. }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8216\'91Top Ten Reasons Why I Should Go to Art School.\u8217\'92}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki smirked. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re siding with }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 him,}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Aiko? I thought you were all about rebelling against parental expectations with me.\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 know,}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 Aiko groaned dramatically, throwing her hands up. \u8220\'93But me arguing with my parents is one thing\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 we argue all the time. }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 You}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  arguing with }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 your}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  parents is another thing entirely.\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 She gave Haruki a pointed look. \u8220\'93Your parents are }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 scary.}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah, look.\u8221\'94 Akihito shot her a skeptical glance. \u8220\'93Tell me you\u8217\'92ve at least discussed this with one of them.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki smirked but didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t slow her pace. \u8220\'93I talked with my mom,\u8221\'94 she said simply.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito narrowed his eyes. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And your dad?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki shrugged. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93He wasn\u8217\'92t around,\u8221\'94 she said, her voice casual. \u8220\'93But I don\u8217\'92t think he\u8217\'92d care.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito let out a sharp breath, running a hand through his hair. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re crazy,\u8221\'94 he muttered. \u8220\'93Do you even hear yourself? Your dad\u8217\'92s not just some businessman\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 he\u8217\'92s the CEO of a major automotive company. Of }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 course}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d care!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki stopped in her tracks and turned to face him, her expression calm but unwavering. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No, he wasn\u8217\'92t around,\u8221\'94 she said, emphasizing each word. \u8220\'93He\u8217\'92s }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 never}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  around. He\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s too busy with work to care about what I do.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito frowned but didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t argue. Aiko shifted uncomfortably beside them, her gaze darting between the two.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki sighed, gripping her sketchbook tighter. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Look, I know it sounds reckless, but I can\u8217\'92t keep waiting for their approval. If I do, I\u8217\'92ll never get to live my life. I have to take this step, even if it\u8217\'92s scary.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s jaw tightened. \u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s not the point. You might not care about what }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 they}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  think, but they\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ll definitely care about }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 you}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  going against them. And your parents aren\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t exactly the \u8216\'91let it go\u8217\'92 type.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki nodded, a small smile tugging at her lips. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I know. But I\u8217\'92ll figure it out. I always do.\u8221\'94}
