\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 As Haruki sled the door open to the arts club room, the room was buzzing with energy as club members prepared for their weekly }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 plein air}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  session. Easels were being adjusted, canvases stacked, sketchbooks flipped open, and tubes of paint uncapped. The faint scent of oil paint and graphite filled the air, mixing with the chatter of students discussing the best locations for today\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s outing.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 At the center of it all, like a captain amidst a storm of creativity, stood Makoto, the Art Club\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s president. He was giving instructions to a group of younger students, gesturing animatedly with a charcoal stick in hand.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 But as Haruki scanned the room, something unusual caught her eye\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 someone who definitely wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t a regular in the Art Club.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mrs. Kitagawa.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki stiffened. What was the school counselor doing here?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko and Akihito entered behind her, the three of them exchanging wary glances. Before Haruki could dwell on it, Makoto\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s voice rang out over the hum of activity.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Haruki! Mrs. Kitagawa wants to see you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 A murmur of curiosity rippled through the club, but everyone quickly went back to their preparations.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki exhaled, schooling her expression into something neutral. She slung her bag off her shoulder, setting it down in the corner, before making her way toward Mrs. Kitagawa.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki crossed her arms, shifting her weight slightly as she faced Mrs. Kitagawa. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If this is about my Career Plans form, I swear I submitted it this morning,\u8221\'94 she said, forcing a small, confident smile. \u8220\'93I didn\u8217\'92t forget.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mrs. Kitagawa nodded. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yes, I received it.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki tilted her head. Then what is it?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But that\u8217\'92s not why I called you here,\u8221\'94 Mrs. Kitagawa continued, her tone even, measured.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s stomach dipped slightly. Her fingers curled around the strap of her bag. \u8220\'93Then\u8230\'85 why?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 There was a pause.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mrs. Kitagawa exhaled softly before delivering the news. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Your father is in the teacher\u8217\'92s office. He\u8217\'92s here to pick you up for a family occasion.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki felt the words before she fully processed them\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 a strange weight settling in her chest, as if the air had thickened around her.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Her grip tightened on her bag. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mrs. Kitagawa\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s expression remained gentle but firm. \u8220\'93Your father requested that you leave with him immediately.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s pulse quickened. This had to be a mistake. Her father never just }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 showed up}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  like this. He was supposed to be }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 too busy}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  for things like unannounced visits.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 And today\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 today}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 was the club\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 plein air}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  session.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But I have club activities,\u8221\'94 she argued, her voice steadier than she felt. \u8220\'93We\u8217\'92re heading out for }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 plein air}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  today, and Makoto needs my help with the first-years\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 I }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 can\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  be absent.\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I understand,\u8221\'94 Mrs. Kitagawa said, her voice soft but unwavering. \u8220\'93But this is your father\u8217\'92s request.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Request.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 No, this wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t a }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 request.}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  It was an order.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The weight in her chest sank lower. There was no room for negotiation here.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Slowly, reluctantly, she turned toward Akihito. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Can you cover for me?\u8221\'94 she asked, her voice quieter now. \u8220\'93Help Makoto with the first-years?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Akihito hesitated for a fraction of a second before nodding. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah. Don\u8217\'92t worry about it.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki swallowed, then reached for her bag. The excitement from earlier\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 the rush of stepping into the clubroom, the anticipation of an afternoon spent outside with paint and sunlight\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 was gone, drained out of her like ink washing away in the rain.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Without another word, she followed Mrs. Kitagawa toward the door.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Aiko and Akihito stood in silence, watching her go. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 -o-}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki trailed behind Mrs. Kitagawa, her steps slower than they needed to be, as if dragging her feet might somehow delay the inevitable.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 This is it\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8230\'85}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The thought settled heavily in her chest, dull and suffocating. She watched as the club rooms passed by\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 each doorway revealing glimpses of students lost in their passions.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The soft melody of a violin drifted from the music room, accompanied by the occasional stumble of fingers pressing the wrong note. Someone in the literature club gestured wildly as they debated over a novel, voices overlapping in a lively discussion. Inside the manga club, students huddled around a table, sketching, erasing, redrawing\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 completely immersed in their craft.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 They were all doing what they loved. Pursuing what made them }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 feel alive.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki swallowed hard. }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 And I\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92m walking the green mile.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 She felt it with every step\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 like she was heading toward something final, something irreversible. As if, the moment she reached that office, she wouldn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t just be facing her father.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 She\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d be facing the end of her dream.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Her fingers tightened around the strap of her bag.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 No. Not yet.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 She kept walking, but the weight in her chest only grew heavier.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Haruki stepped into the teacher\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s office, her breath catching for a split second.}
